":"要係官網先有得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd603fe37980f96884ed43b3eaa9f1cc3c77cf0b","tid":1577660,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1cab0565e9d376aaa5090a5c948e2b4a4cfa953","tid":1577660,"uid":92680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T00:31:21.000Z","msg":"Castrovilli好似幾好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:07:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rD5ewQnIPEM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DrD5ewQnIPEM&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Mg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=37bceb1d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rD5ewQnIPEM</a>"},{"pid":"1eb8566daf864560b17844905983c8c7cdf8d40b","tid":1577660,"uid":64525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"以前鐘意Rossi<br />\n而家鍾意Chiesa"},{"pid":"6c6d967e90619708bc5c8ac1f2b6530441e9cf76","tid":1577660,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1eb8566daf864560b17844905983c8c7cdf8d40b","tid":1577660,"uid":64525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T16:18:44.000Z","msg":"以前鐘意Rossi<br />\n而家鍾意Chiesa"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:17:06.000Z","msg":"一樣<br />\nRossi衣家變左free agent<br />\n其實簽番佢番黎打下都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a2686869818614c4f3d3048472f227bf02f392","tid":1577660,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:27:11.000Z","msg":"Montella: &rdquo;I won&rsquo;t sleep tonight.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FrSadHt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFrSadHt.jpg&h=798e9a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n與阿塔蘭塔（Atalanta）2-2戰平後，文森佐&middot;蒙特拉（Vincenzo Montella）&ldquo;今晚不會入睡&rdquo;，但他感到佛羅倫薩在艱難的比賽上表現出色。<br />\n<br />\n紫百合4場僅得2分排名在意甲聯賽榜尾，已經連續在18輪意甲聯賽中均未獲勝。<br />\n<br />\n他們在對陣亞特蘭大的比賽中以2-0領先，但在比賽的最後幾秒鐘又被2-2的比分扳平比分。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們與那不勒斯，尤文圖斯和亞特蘭大隊交手，他們上賽季排名前三，我們對這些強隊的表現都非常出色，&rdquo;蒙泰拉在意大利天空體育上堅持說。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我們從所有這些比賽中獲得更多經驗與得益，我們應該以這首幾場硬仗球隊的精彩表演和精神士氣而感到榮譽。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;如果我們能夠在客場迫使像亞特蘭大這樣的球隊在最後一秒才能扳平得分，那就意味著我們並沒有太壞。我今晚不能睡覺，與此同時，我必須審視這支佛羅倫薩隊的整個旅程，我們走在正確的道路上。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;一旦到達球賽尾端，這是非常複雜的，球隊因傷勢而不得不進行一些替換。我們知道亞特蘭大隊非常擅長捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;我必須看著這些積極的因素，因為其實球隊在大部分比賽中都表演出色亦很穩定。&rdquo;"},{"pid":"aaebf40662ade1e4526ddef2107d74932d540fb1","tid":1577660,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"ATALANTA 2-2 FIORENTINA<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YShJyVl2ihE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYShJyVl2ihE&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Mg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=84cab9be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YShJyVl2ihE</a>"},{"pid":"355c39047d909fd847d2817297b50abc8f002fd9","tid":1577660,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aaebf40662ade1e4526ddef2107d74932d540fb1","tid":1577660,"uid":9714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:30:46.000Z","msg":"ATALANTA 2-2 FIORENTINA<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/YShJyVl2ihE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FYShJyVl2ihE&d=RXc9xvVhXBFlPE4DV6Zf5Mg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=84cab9be\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/YShJyVl2ihE</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T14:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eLsA9kr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeLsA9kr.png&h=e7ddc09f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1d798770383467ee65220b083e59ffc982d0c9e6","tid":1577660,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T15:17:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/BmNoWxm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBmNoWxm.gif&h=5bfea83a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"257ec761c7de47ce113f0beaa31b8f10569c85af","